	(text "This board for the most part relies on the Heltec WiFi LoRa 32(V3) development board,\nwhich in itself contains:\n- A built-in battery interface and BMS with USB charging\n- On-board LoRa and WiFi support\n- A GPIO-controlled +3V3 source V_EXT (High by default, disabled by driving GPIO36 low)\n- Good RF and low-power circuitry"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 19.05 24.13 0)
